creating node project

- mkdir newfileyay
- cd into it 
- code . 
- create entry point file... usually index.js
- NPM init -y //to install and skip
- nodemon to see code in action
- touch .gitignore

installing 3rd party modules
- npm i -g nameofnode  //to install globally
- npm i nameofnode //to install locally
- add node_modules  and anything else you want git to ignore
